news.news: Beasley is in the Pistons' starting lineup against the Trail Blazers on Monday, Omari Sankofa II of the Detroit Free Press reports.
news.analysis: Beasley will make his ninth start of the regular season Monday due to the absence of Ausar Thompson (illness). Over his last 10 outings, Beasley has averaged 17.1 points, 3.0 rebounds, 1.8 assists and 1.0 steals over 27.6 minutes per contest.

news.headline: Drains three treys Saturday
news.news: Beasley ended with 23 points (8-17 FG, 6-14 3Pt, 1-2 FT), two rebounds, one assist and three steals over 33 minutes during Saturday's 119-105 win over the Timberwolves.
